search_results.title: About
search_results.snippet: Dr. Sammy founder and director of the Ramsey Research Foundation graduated with a Bachelor of Science in Entomology from Cornell University in 2011.

search_results.title: Sammy Zahran, Professor - College of Liberal Arts
search_results.snippet: Sammy Zahran is a Professor in the Department of Economics. Sammy is also a Professor in the Department of Epidemiology in the Colorado School of Public Health.

search_results.title: Sammy Smooha
search_results.snippet: Sammy Smooha (Hebrew: סמי סמוחה; born 1941) is a Professor of Sociology at the University of Haifa. Sammy Smooha. סמי סמוחה. Born, 1941.
